{"tid":2285724,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[千人計劃]小心中大董咚博士指導的基因研究","createTime":"2020-11-14T10:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T10:57:29.000Z","uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9a7cc2f92bd0b1ca59bd5b96d06aea4aaef0d2b0","tid":2285724,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T10:47:11.000Z","msg":"[千人計劃]小心中大董咚博士指導的基因研究<br />\n原貼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2285713/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2285713/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<del>香港成年人 基因素養 程度嘅大型研究<br />\n基因素養指的是對基因或遺傳學原理有足夠的知識和理解，牽涉對基因原理的態度，能為個人健康或安康做出明智的決定，並有效地參與有關基因或遺傳問題的<span class=\"xx-large\">社會決策</span>。</del><br />\n<br />\nProf. Dong DONG畢業於U of Minnesota<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sphpc.cuhk.edu.hk/dongdong?lang=zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sphpc.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fdongdong%3Flang%3Dzh&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=85c437c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sphpc.cuhk.edu.hk/dongdong?lang=zh</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cfa.shufe-cec.com/p/32.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfa.shufe-cec.com%2Fp%2F32.html&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=e102672a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cfa.shufe-cec.com/p/32.html</a><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">知名校友/師兄係田國強, 千人計劃首批專家, 位階好高</span></span><br />\n-------------------------------------------<br />\n1)香港警魔,深圳關口係無合理理由搶香港人基因資料,特別係異見人士<br />\n2)點解香港政府故意唔封關玩到疫情爆發再強推強制檢測?<br />\n3) 中國都大把人, 香港人基因特別?狗共千方百計攪香港基因庫原因?"},{"pid":"50ec08643dd077ec0f8d2cea4650b9dcdad052e8","tid":2285724,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T10:50:17.000Z","msg":"玩到送IPHONE<br />\n<br />\n下一步香港政府可能攪自願驗身<br />\n驗完買自願醫保計劃有折都似<br />\n<br />\n你願意交DNA真係咩柒都送比你<br />\n你屋企有一條友貪小便宜交基因都奶野"},{"pid":"7a1294229caacd821084b9a6ff4baa6b371a96cd","tid":2285724,"uid":189234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,